Mera mood aaj kharab tha. Mi fakta shant: Mi tula call karnar hota. Tumhara number band aa raha tha.
Kal college mein bahut maza aaya. Mi mitranchya sobat canteen la gelo hoto.
Tujhi madat khup mahatvachi hoti. Tumne sach me support diya.
Mi job sathi form bharla hota. Lekin mujhe call nahi aaya.
Mi shevti shortlist zhalo. Interview bahut acha gaya.
Majhe gharache sagle log ekatra bhetayla aale hote. Humne milke dinner kiya.
Mi office madhe gelo hoto. Ghar par koi bhi nahi tha.
Mala navi mobile ghechi hoti. Lekin mummy ne mana kiya.
Tu ekdam smart distoy. Tumhara confidence bahut inspiring hai.
Kal party madhe khup maja jhali. Sab log bohot enjoy kar rahe the.
Mi dusrya city madhe shift zhalo. Mujhe yahaan ka mahaul bilkul pasand nahi.
Tula baghun khup changla vatla. Tum hamesha ache lagte ho.
Tichya bolnyavar bharosa nahi karu shakat. Uski baatein badalte rehti hain.
Aaj gharat khup shant vatat hota. Sab log mandir gaye the.
Tyane mala maaf kela. Main apni galti maan gaya.
Mi khup mehnat kela. Lekin usne madat karne se inkaar kiya.
Amhi ganpati utsav khup utsahat sadhavla. Sabne milke pooja kiya.
To khup samajdaar aahe. Par uska gussa kabhi kabhi zyada hota hai.
Tula navin job lagli. Saglyanna gharat khup anand zala.
